title: Bridgers Leaders Break the Exodus 90 Fast
description:
A number of key leaders from the Bridges of Meaning Discord Server participated in the Exodus 90 Extended Lenten Fast. Now that Easter is here I have them in to talk about their experience. 

Conversations with Job https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLYSXopxC8Z9to_1IQWB9gNjYaRfzvPLad

Prayer, Asceticism and Fasting: to intensify and lengthen the Lent experience

Eric, Catholic Priest in North Dakota

South eastern North Dakota, 8000 people In it. 

Prayer, fraternity and asceticism

Commit to a holy hour every day, nightly examine, how to do that
Fraternity: Anchor to check in with every day
Weekly fraternity meeting: happened over Discord
Asceticism: fast on Wed. and Friday, Full meal and two snacks, no meat on Wed and Friday, no alcohol, sweets, no unnecessary 

Only listen to music that lifts your soul to God

Have a more intense Lenten experience, deepen faith, only trusting what God has

Had to write a "why"

January 4 was the first day, before the 6th

Felt starved from "me" time

What surprised you, what disappointed you, what did you learn about yourself? What did you learn about the faith? 

What surprises hit you when you came out? 

Bridgers Break Their Exodus 90 Fast

Being that Priest/Victim: Fulton Sheen, priest is not his own

Tim Keller, Hope in Times of Fear

Necessity of Christ for a broken world

Limiting in order to create abundance for others

Discord link. Good for just a few days. Check with more recent videos for a fresh link. https://discord.gg/MZyXFVc6
